resources.string: Faka ikhadi lesikoloto ukuze ukwazi ukuthenga izinhlelo zokusebenza, amabhuku, kanye namamuvi e-Android Market.
Iphutha livelile ngenkathi ixhumana namaseva e-Google. Sicela uzame futhi.
I-Market idinga idatha yasemuva ukuva ivunyelwe.
Tshela i-Market uma uthola lolu hlelo lokusebenza noma lesi sikrini njengesinokuqukethwe okungathandeki.
